---
// Enhanced ClinicalTrustSection.astro (Complete)
---

<section
  class="bg-gradient-to-b from-white to-[#f8f9fa] py-20 px-6 sm:px-12 relative overflow-hidden"
  data-aos="fade-up"
>
  <!-- Abstract decorative elements -->
  <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-full z-0">
    <div
      class="absolute -top-20 -right-20 w-64 h-64 bg-[#003087]/5 rounded-full blur-3xl"
    >
    </div>
    <div
      class="absolute -bottom-20 -left-20 w-64 h-64 bg-[#cc9933]/5 rounded-full blur-3xl"
    >
    </div>
    <div
      class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-full h-full max-w-4xl"
    >
      <svg
        width="100%"
        height="100%"
        viewBox="0 0 200 200"
        xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
        class="opacity-[0.02]"
      >
        <path
          fill="#003087"
          d="M37.5,-65.1C46.9,-55.3,51.1,-41.3,57.2,-29C63.3,-16.6,71.4,-5.8,72.8,6.1C74.3,18,69.2,31,59.8,38.5C50.5,45.9,36.8,47.9,24.2,53.3C11.6,58.7,0,67.5,-14.6,71.2C-29.2,74.9,-46.9,73.5,-57.9,64.1C-68.9,54.8,-73.3,37.6,-73.3,21.9C-73.3,6.3,-68.9,-7.8,-66.2,-24.5C-63.4,-41.3,-62.4,-60.8,-52.4,-70.6C-42.5,-80.4,-23.7,-80.5,-7.3,-70.7C9.1,-60.8,28.1,-74.8,37.5,-65.1Z"
          transform="translate(100 100)"></path>
      </svg>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto text-center relative z-10">
    <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-3 mb-3">
      <span class="h-px w-12 bg-[#cc9933]"></span>
      <span class="text-[#cc9933] uppercase tracking-wider text-sm font-bold"
        >Clinical Excellence</span
      >
      <span class="h-px w-12 bg-[#cc9933]"></span>
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-semibold text-[#003087] mb-6">
      The Experts Behind Every Scan
    </h2>

    <p
      class="text-lg md:text-xl text-[#003087] leading-relaxed max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-12"
    >
      Your scan isn't just run through a machine â€” it's carefully interpreted by
      board-certified radiologists who specialize in diagnostic imaging. We
      ensure clinical excellence at every step.
    </p>

    <!-- Credentials grid -->
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-12">
      <div class="credential-card" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">
        <div class="credential-icon">
          <svg
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
            class="h-8 w-8"
            fill="none"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            stroke="currentColor"
          >
            <path
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              stroke-width="2"
              d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"
            ></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="credential-title">Board-Certified Radiologists</h3>
        <p class="credential-description">
          Every scan is interpreted by radiologists who have passed rigorous
          board certification exams and maintain ongoing medical education.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="credential-card" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="200">
        <div class="credential-icon">
          <svg
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
            class="h-8 w-8"
            fill="none"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            stroke="currentColor"
          >
            <path
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              stroke-width="2"
              d="M19.428 15.428a2 2 0 00-1.022-.547l-2.387-.477a6 6 0 00-3.86.517l-.318.158a6 6 0 01-3.86.517L6.05 15.21a2 2 0 00-1.806.547M8 4h8l-1 1v5.172a2 2 0 00.586 1.414l5 5c1.26 1.26.367 3.414-1.415 3.414H4.828c-1.782 0-2.674-2.154-1.414-3.414l5-5A2 2 0 009 10.172V5L8 4z"
            ></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="credential-title">Subspecialty Expertise</h3>
        <p class="credential-description">
          Many of our radiologists have completed additional fellowship training
          in specialized areas like neuroradiology, musculoskeletal imaging, or
          body imaging.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="credential-card" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="300">
        <div class="credential-icon">
          <svg
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
            class="h-8 w-8"
            fill="none"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            stroke="currentColor"
          >
            <path
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              stroke-width="2"
              d="M19 21V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v16m14 0h2m-2 0h-5m-9 0H3m2 0h5M9 7h1m-1 4h1m4-4h1m-1 4h1m-5 10v-5a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v5m-4 0h4"
            ></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="credential-title">Accredited Facilities</h3>
        <p class="credential-description">
          We partner exclusively with imaging centers that meet strict
          accreditation standards for equipment quality, safety protocols, and
          staff qualifications.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Quality commitment -->
    <div
      class="quality-banner p-6 md:p-8 bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm"
      data-aos="fade-up"
    >
      <h3 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-[#003087]">
        Our Quality Commitment
      </h3>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div class="quality-item">
          <div class="quality-icon">
            <svg
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              class="h-6 w-6"
              fill="none"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              stroke="currentColor"
            >
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="2"
                d="M9 5H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2M9 5a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2M9 5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2"
              ></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h4 class="quality-title">Scan Protocol Standardization</h4>
          <p class="quality-description">
            We ensure consistent high-quality scans by standardizing scanning
            protocols across all our partner imaging centers.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="quality-item">
          <div class="quality-icon">
            <svg
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              class="h-6 w-6"
              fill="none"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              stroke="currentColor"
            >
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="2"
                d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h4 class="quality-title">Rapid Results Delivery</h4>
          <p class="quality-description">
            Most scan results are available within 24-48 hours, compared to the
            industry standard of 3-5 days.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="quality-item">
          <div class="quality-icon">
            <svg
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              class="h-6 w-6"
              fill="none"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              stroke="currentColor"
            >
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="2"
                d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"
              ></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h4 class="quality-title">Quality Assurance Process</h4>
          <p class="quality-description">
            We implement regular quality reviews to ensure all imaging centers
            consistently meet our high standards.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="quality-item">
          <div class="quality-icon">
            <svg
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              class="h-6 w-6"
              fill="none"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              stroke="currentColor"
            >
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="2"
                d="M12 6V4m0 2a2 2 0 100 4m0-4a2 2 0 110 4m-6 8a2 2 0 100-4m0 4a2 2 0 110-4m0 4v2m0-6V4m6 6v10m6-2a2 2 0 100-4m0 4a2 2 0 110-4m0 4v2m0-6V4"
              ></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h4 class="quality-title">Advanced Technology</h4>
          <p class="quality-description">
            We only partner with facilities that use current-generation,
            high-field imaging equipment for optimal diagnostic quality.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Expert quote -->
    <div
      class="expert-quote mt-12 p-8 bg-[#f0f4f9] rounded-xl border border-[#e6e9f0] relative"
      data-aos="fade-up"
    >
      <div
        class="absolute -top-5 left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2 bg-[#cc9933] text-white w-10 h-10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center"
      >
        <svg
          xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
          class="h-6 w-6"
          fill="none"
          viewBox="0 0 24 24"
          stroke="currentColor"
        >
          <path
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round"
            stroke-width="2"
            d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <blockquote class="text-lg md:text-xl italic text-[#003087] mb-6">
        "When it's your health on the line, guesswork isn't good enough. You
        deserve precision. You deserve peace of mind."
      </blockquote>
      <div class="text-sm font-medium text-[#003087]/70">
        - USRad Medical Advisory Board
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .credential-card {
    background-color: white;
    border-radius: 1rem;
    padding: 2rem;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
    height: 100%;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    border-bottom: 3px solid #cc9933;
  }

  .credential-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
    box-shadow: 0 12px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
  }

  .credential-icon {
    width: 56px;
    height: 56px;
    background-color: #003087;
    color: white;
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    margin: 0 auto 1.25rem;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .credential-card:hover .credential-icon {
    background-color: #cc9933;
    transform: scale(1.05);
  }

  .credential-title {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #003087;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .credential-description {
    color: #003087;
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .quality-item {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: flex-start;
    text-align: left;
  }

  .quality-icon {
    width: 40px;
    height: 40px;
    background-color: #f0f4f9;
    color: #003087;
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .quality-item:hover .quality-icon {
    background-color: #cc9933;
    color: white;
  }

  .quality-title {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #003087;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .quality-description {
    color: #003087;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .expert-quote {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
  }
</style>
